  <scopecontent id="aspace_99122fa7ea53955820ba6ccf3d997ba8">
    <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
<p>The collection consists largely of correspondence received by Mates in his capacity as commander of the Bay Area Post of the Veterans of the Abraham Lincoln Brigade (VALB).  Along with regular mailings from the VALB national office and notices from the Bay Area Post are newsletters and notices from Spanish Civil War veterans in Canada and in Europe.  There is also a small amount of personal correspondence from other U.S. veterans, including Steve Nelson, Robert Reed and Sana Goldblatt.  One envelope contains a few original photos and reproductions of photos from 1937-38 in Spain.</p>  </scopecontent>
